SUMMARY:Sober Game Night
DESCRIPTION:Sober Game Night!\nFellowship • Food • Fun! \nWhen:\nLast Friday of the Month\n6:00 PM – 8:00 PM \nLocation:\nSCIF Meeting Hall\n750 Mendocino Ave #9\nSanta Rosa\, CA 95401 \n\nPlay & Win\nJoin us for a fun evening of games\, fellowship\, and snacks in a sober environment.\nEnjoy board games\, cards\, and friendly competition with the community. \nBring snacks while listening to AA Speaker Tapes! \n\nBoard games\nCard games\nCommunity fellowship\nSnacks to share\n\nEveryone is welcome!
URL:https://sonomacountyaa.org/event/sober-game-night/
LOCATION:SCIF Meeting Hall\, 750 Mendocino Avenue\, Suite 9\, Santa Rosa\, CA\, 95401\, United States
END:VEVENT
