SUMMARY:46th Annual Pillsbury Camp Out
DESCRIPTION:Outdoor fun and fellowship\, the week of May 11 – 17th. \nThe big meeting is on Saturday night\, May 16th. \nOvernight Use-No Reservation\nSingle Site: $16 per night\nAdditional Vehicle Fee: $3 per vehicle per night\n$1 per pet per night\nBoating launch fee: $5\nCash or Check Only
