SUMMARY:Monte Rio Fellowship Spring Potluck / BBQ
DESCRIPTION:2nd Annual Spring Potluck / Barbecue\nAfter the Noon Meeting \nDate:\nSunday\, May 17 \nJoin us for an afternoon of fellowship\, food\, and fun at our annual spring gathering! \n\nLocation\nMonte Rio Fellowship\n(the former St. Andrew’s Church)\n20329 Hwy. 116 \n\nWhat to Expect\n\nPotluck dishes\nBarbecue\nFellowship and community\n\nAll are welcome!
